3eHow many contacts logged by a control panel user.\n- \u003cb\u003eMost Donations:\u003c/b\u003e How many donations made by a person.\n- \u003cb\u003eMost Earned Social Capital:\u003c/b\u003e Amount of social capital earned by a person. Use social capital to measure actions that are not represented in the default leaderboard types. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Emails Sent: \u003c/b\u003eHow many emails are sent by a person to one of your broadcasters. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Followers: \u003c/b\u003eHow many followers a person has acquired in your nation. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Donations:\u003c/b\u003e How many donations recruited by a person. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Donors: \u003c/b\u003eHow many donors recruited by a person. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Endorsements:\u003c/b\u003e How many endorsements recruited by a person on your website’s endorsement page.\n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Feedback:\u003c/b\u003e How many feedback posts recruited by a person to your website’s feedback page by a person. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Pledgers:\u003c/b\u003e How many pledgers recruited by a person to your nation. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Pledges: \u003c/b\u003eHow many pledges recruited by a person to your nation. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited RSVPs: \u003c/b\u003eHow many RSVPs recruited by a person to your nation. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Signatures: \u003c/b\u003eHow many petition signatures recruited by a person on your website’s petition page. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Signups:\u003c/b\u003e How many signups recruited by a person to you nation. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Suggestions: \u003c/b\u003eHow many suggestions recruited by a person to your website’s suggestion page. \n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Survey Responses: \u003c/b\u003eHow many survey responses recruited by a person to your nation.\n- \u003cb\u003eMost Recruited Volunteers:\u003c/b\u003e How many volunteers recruited by a person to your nation. \n- \u003